==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whatso
<hw>What"so</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>indef. pron.</pos> <def>Whatsoever;
whosoever; whatever; anything that.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Whatso</qex> he were, of high or low estate.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Whatso</qex> the heaven in his wide vault contains.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whatsoe'er</ent>⟦br⟧
